这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 6026, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 609423, "username": "programApe", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/programApe", "website": "https://allbs.cn", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "chenqi92", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_mini.png?m=1760316869", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_normal.png?m=1760316869", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_large.png?m=1760316869", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_xlarge.png?m=1760316869", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_xxlarge.png?m=1760316869", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c9b/664e/609423_xxxlarge.png?m=1760316869", "created": 1672983514, "last_modified": 1760316869, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ryan0966", "last_touched": 1777560732, "title": "一个主要用于家庭影音资源管理软件，支持 ios、android、macos、windows 等，补充下截图。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1209606", "created": 1777519866, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 主要功能\r\n功能包含影视、音乐、图书、相册等，主要用于家庭 nas 资源管理。可以关联下载器（ qBittorrent 这种），pt 站（馒头这种自定义请求头和其他站的 cookie 方式接入），媒体资源管理类（ NASTool 这种）。数据来源包括家庭 nas （群晖等 nas ，绿联和飞牛占位等公开接入 api ）、webdav 、smb 、emby 、plex 、jellyfin 等。其他辅助的一些刮削、字幕、软解硬解、投屏等等，主打的就是功能多，bug 多。\r\n\r\n# 概括\r\n现在状态是能用但不易用，功能多但界面丑。曾经踩过不少坑，如果碰到什么问题可以找找思路。\r\n\r\n# 一些截图：\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/067b17d8152f8b514bdc979853b5ff55.png)\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/7183e33fb6af7f88f2d9793a890d1a3e.png)\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/2509128918beb534c06f1f971074fa53.jpg)\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/602eb0553cb0a73cd1182f21edcb592c.jpg)\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/ce0f3b75b935111238661939939abf10.png)\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/269b8b60c7661ab033aa061c7a86056b.jpg)\r\n\r\n# 开源地址\r\n[https://github.com/chenqi92/my-nas]( https://github.com/chenqi92/my-nas)\r\n\r\n# 音乐功能单独抽出来上架了\r\nappstore 搜**猿音**，音乐刮削功能需要导入 json 实现规避版权问题，可以留**邮箱 base**，我有一个朋友可以发给你。\r\n\r\n![]( https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/9a8e7a9514137e786fe9e89b3dd2e310.png)\r\n\r\n# 开源地址\r\n[https://github.com/chenqi92/primuse]( https://github.com/chenqi92/primuse)\r\n\r\nPS:如果对你有用，并且有什么想法可以提 issue ，让我知道真的有人在用，有动力继续开发下去", "content_rendered": "<h1>主要功能</h1>\n<p>功能包含影视、音乐、图书、相册等，主要用于家庭 nas 资源管理。可以关联下载器（ qBittorrent 这种），pt 站（馒头这种自定义请求头和其他站的 cookie 方式接入），媒体资源管理类（ NASTool 这种）。数据来源包括家庭 nas （群晖等 nas ，绿联和飞牛占位等公开接入 api ）、webdav 、smb 、emby 、plex 、jellyfin 等。其他辅助的一些刮削、字幕、软解硬解、投屏等等，主打的就是功能多，bug 多。</p>\n<h1>概括</h1>\n<p>现在状态是能用但不易用，功能多但界面丑。曾经踩过不少坑，如果碰到什么问题可以找找思路。</p>\n<h1>一些截图：</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/067b17d8152f8b514bdc979853b5ff55.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/7183e33fb6af7f88f2d9793a890d1a3e.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/2509128918beb534c06f1f971074fa53.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/602eb0553cb0a73cd1182f21edcb592c.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/ce0f3b75b935111238661939939abf10.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/269b8b60c7661ab033aa061c7a86056b.jpg\"/></p>\n<h1>开源地址</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/chenqi92/my-nas\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/chenqi92/my-nas</a></p>\n<h1>音乐功能单独抽出来上架了</h1>\n<p>appstore 搜<strong>猿音</strong>，音乐刮削功能需要导入 json 实现规避版权问题，可以留<strong>邮箱 base</strong>，我有一个朋友可以发给你。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://nas.allbs.cn:8888/cloudpic/2026/04/9a8e7a9514137e786fe9e89b3dd2e310.png\"/></p>\n<h1>开源地址</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/chenqi92/primuse\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/chenqi92/primuse</a></p>\n<p>PS:如果对你有用，并且有什么想法可以提 issue ，让我知道真的有人在用，有动力继续开发下去</p>\n", "last_modified": 1777519866, "replies": 43, "id": 1209606}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2d6c/c4b2/507_large.png?m=1768280131", "name": "cv", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2d6c/c4b2/507_normal.png?m=1768280131", "title": "求职", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/cv", "topics": 9021, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎在这里发布自己的求职简历。", "title_alternative": "CV", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2d6c/c4b2/507_mini.png?m=1768280131", "stars": 1785, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 507, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 657135, "username": "1094705286", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/1094705286", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a649e1c826c4cb260b64d4f8d3a81809?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a649e1c826c4cb260b64d4f8d3a81809?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a649e1c826c4cb260b64d4f8d3a81809?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1698732077, "last_modified": 1777519303, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "crynocry", "last_touched": 1777557993, "title": "毕业了朋友们，今日 Last Day", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/12096